## QUALITY CHECKLIST (run before completing each phase)

- [ ] `flutter analyze` returns 0 errors, 0 warnings
- [ ] All colors use `AppColors.*` constants
- [ ] All text styles use `AppTypography.*` constants
- [ ] All async operations show loading state
- [ ] All error cases handled and shown to user
- [ ] No hardcoded strings (use `AppStrings.*` or inline is okay for single-use)
- [ ] Animations use flutter_animate with appropriate duration
- [ ] Hive boxes pre-opened in main.dart
- [ ] Riverpod providers tested with manual state changes

---

## FINAL DEMO READINESS CHECK

Before declaring the app demo-ready:

- [ ] Onboarding → Home flow works end to end
- [ ] AI Chat sends message and shows Meera's response
- [ ] Voice mode: mic tap → transcript → AI response spoken aloud
- [ ] DIY Checker: 3 ingredients → score appears with animation
- [ ] Habit tracker: tap to complete → confetti shows
- [ ] Insights screen: charts load with data
- [ ] Context is injected: Meera mentions user's name and habits in responses
- [ ] App survives kill + relaunch with all data intact (Hive persistence)
- [ ] No crashes on any screen
- [ ] Demo seed data pre-populated (Priya's profile + habits + food log)
